videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano runs the QB keeper and sneaks it in for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tennessee QB Guarantano scores the games first TD

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano lauches a deep ball to Marquez Callaway who makes a leaping grab for 42-yards.
videos.headline: Tennessees' Guarantano shows off arm on big play

videos.description: Keon Howard fires a desperation pass on 3rd & 18  to Korey Robertson and he makes an acrobatic catch, then runs for a 70-yard gain.
videos.headline: Southern Mississippi WR Robertson gives offense life with big catch

videos.description: Butch Jones says Jarrett Guarantano has been through this and he displayed great toughness in coming back in the game.
videos.headline: Tennessee Coach Jones talks about QB Guarantano getting hurt

videos.description: Keon Howard attempts a pass to his receiver but CB Emmanuel Moseley intercepts the ball and returns it 19-yards to put Tennessee into good field position.
videos.headline: Volunteers defense gets a huge turnover

videos.description: John Kelly takes the hand-off and goes up the gut of the defense, while throwing a mean stiff-arm to score a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Volunteers RB Kelly extends the lead with TD

videos.description: Keon Howard is strip sacked by DE Darrell Taylor. Tennessee gets the ball back, making it two straight drives of turnovers.
videos.headline: The Volunteers stingy D creating turnovers

videos.description: John Kelly, punches it in from 3-yards out for another touchdown. He has scored on back-to-back drives. Tennessee now leads 24-3.
videos.headline: Volunteers RB Kelly scores 2nd TD

videos.description: Golden Eagles' backup QB Kwadra Griggs comes in the game and scores a 1-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Southern Mississippi not done yet, after rushing TD

videos.description: John Kelly says it felt good to be back with all his teammates. He also added that he loved being the workhorse for the team and it was great to get the win over Southern Mississippi.
videos.headline: Volunteers' RB Kelly talks about how it felt to be back after injury

videos.description: Jordan Rodgers and Tom Hart previews SEC week for Tennessee and says they need to correct some offensive issues as well as put up a lot of points against Missouri. next week.
videos.headline: Tennessee's impressive run game leads to victory
